== Properties

--- font: gpointer (Read)

    The selected Gtk::Font

--- font-name: String (Read/Write)

    Name of the selected font

--- label-font-size: Integer (Read/Write)

    Font size for label in font info mode

--- mode: Gnome::FontPickerMode (Read/Write)

    The mode of operation of the font picker

--- preview-text: String (Read/Write)

    Preview text shown in the dialog

--- show-size: true or false (Read/Write)

    Show size in font info mode

--- title: String (Read/Write)

    The title of the selection dialog box

--- use-font-in-label: true or false (Read/Write)

    Use font in the label in font info mode

